battle_df <- read_csv("nps_battles.csv", show_col_types = FALSE)
battle_df <- battle_df %>% 
  mutate(
    significance_numeric = case_when(
      significance == 'A' ~ 4,
      significance == 'B' ~ 3,
      significance == 'C' ~ 2,
      significance == 'D' ~ 1
    )
  )
